message: Yesterday was the planning meeting for Florida National University's Powerhouse Human Trafficking Awareness Walk. It is a true honor to work with so many wonderful people representing Education, Government, Law Enforcement, Local Businesses, Non-Profits and concerned citizens. It is a collective effort to combat human trafficking and to keep our communities safe. Like someone said at the meeting yesterday, "Its more than a Powerhouse, its a PowerMansion." Thank you Rachel Tourgeman and Maria Regueiro for making this possible. This ia only a small fraction of all the wonderful people that were there yesterday.
